			Weather
			Shows the weather on the panel
			by Dennis Tomas

Brief
~~~~~
Weather is a panel-applet that shows the weather. If you click on it, it shows 
the forecast.

Installation
~~~~~~~~~~~~
Get Weather and its submodules from GitHub:

$ git clone --recursive https://github.com/dtomas/Weather

Then drag the Weather app dir to a ROX panel.

